Package org.biohipi.examples

Useful examples for understanding the use of BioHIPI.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AvgRGBImage
    AvgRGBImage is an example of how to manipulate Raster images, such as PNG or JPEG, in BioHIB.
    AvgRGBImage.AvgRGBImageMapper
    Useful class for the phase map.
    AvgRGBImage.AvgRGBImageReducer
    Useful class for the phase reduce.
    CutNiftiImage
    CutNiftiImage is an example of how to manipulate NIfTI images in BioHIB.
    CutNiftiImage.CutNiftiImageMapper
    Useful class for the phase map.
    CutNiftiImage.CutNiftiImageReducer
    Useful class for the phase reduce.
    DicomDumpByName
    DicomDumpByName is an example of how to manipulate DICOM images in BioHIB.
    DicomDumpByName.DicomDumpMapper
    Useful class for the phase map.
    DicomDumpByName.DicomDumpReducer
    Useful class for the phase reduce.
    Voxel3dDicom
    VoxelDicomStack is an example of how to manipulate DICOM images in BioHIB.
    Voxel3dDicom.VoxelMapper
    Useful class for the phase map.
    Voxel3dDicom.VoxelReducer
    Useful class for the phase reduce.
    VoxelNifti
    VoxelNifti is an example of how to manipulate NIfTI images in BioHIB.
    VoxelNifti.VoxelNiftiMapper
    Useful class for the phase map.
    VoxelNifti.VoxelNiftiReduced
    Useful class for the phase reduce.
